		<img src="icon_posticon.gif" border="0" hspace="3"><font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2">Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;07/14/2002&nbsp;:&nbsp; 06:22:31</font>

		&nbsp;<a href="pop_profile.asp?mode=display&amp;id=638"><img src="icon_profile.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Show Profile" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>
 
			&nbsp;<a href="JavaScript:openWindow('pop_mail.asp?id=638')"><img src="icon_email.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Email Poster" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>

        &nbsp;<a href="post.asp?method=TopicQuote&amp;TOPIC_ID=6026&amp;FORUM_ID=6&amp;CAT_ID=1&amp;Forum_Title=The+Great+Necro+Talks+2002&amp;Topic_Title=Why+don%27t+we+have+amiable+faction+with+the+undead%3F"><img src="icon_reply_topic.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Reply with Quote" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>

        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"> I have often wonderered why the Necromancer and Shadowknight classes do not enjoy some kind of faction bonus with the undead. We are told in official documentation from Player's Guides that "the price we pay for power is a social stigma". Well this is all fine and good to be hated and despised in most of Norrath but shouldn't we not be appreciated by the undead with whom we associate with? If we are penalized by Norrathian society for our dealings with the undead then doesn't it stand to reason that we should receive some kind of faction bonus with the undead as compensation?</P><P>After all we are the Masters of the Undead just the same way Beastlords are Lords of the beasts. Druids, rangers and beastlords get some form of amiable faction with animals so there is a precedence for a class based faction bonus. This makes sense that these classes should get a positive faction bonus. They deal with animals and are close with nature. We deal with the undead and dabble in necromancy. After all we are in the business of giving "life" to the undead by reanimating them.</P><P>At the very least we should be indifferent with the undead. Many zones like lowerguk, Befallen, and Hate all have faction that would offset any form potential exploit of undead faction bonus. I just think that this would be one way to Verant could give our class a little "lovin'" and I do think there are solid role-playing reasons that justify this.</P><P>Dornette<BR>60 necromancer<BR>The Nameless</P><P></P><P>Edited by - Dornette on 07/14/2002  06:28:47</font></td>

      </tr>

